Pros:
~ Cute female protagonist;
~ Ok-ish graphics;
~ Ok-ish background music;
~ Nice artwork.

Cons:
~ Overpriced;
~ Bad menu design;
~ Cluncky/floaty controls;
~ Combat becomes boring fast;
~ FPS drops randomly;
~ Bad platform design;
~ Bad checkpoint system - I am talking the fact that if you die, is literally game over, you have to restart from the beggining from the level and do the platforming all over again;
~ No health regeneration system - if you get hit by enemies or traps, you can`t do nothing to regenerate health, so you have to stick with the remaining health for the rest of the game;
~ Terrible voice acting;
~ Terrible writting.
